    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of analog performance. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that has been fully overhauled. Power is transmitted via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally impeccable, with proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension system that retains its original geometry and damping response. Every bushing is tight, and the engine\u2019s compression remains within factory specifications. This is a mechanically flawless example for the discerning driver who values high-revving, naturally aspirated precision.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
