    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the standard for 'mint' condition. This car has been treated as a prized collector's piece rather than a daily driver, spending its life in a climate-controlled garage under a custom cover. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirls, chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Step inside to an interior that is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the cabin still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic feature and driver-assist system functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in peak form, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians at the dealership. We have preserved every service receipt and document since the original purchase. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to own a modern classic in its purest possible state.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
