      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cared for, and drives like an absolute dream. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the retail sticker shock, this is the one! Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
